Sentencas: Subsolidus equilibria in air in the La2O3 -CeO2-Co2O3 system were studied with the aim to obtain information on possible interactions between LaCoO3-based cathode and CeO2-based solid electrolyte in solid oxide fuel cells (SOFC).
